author: IANS
title: Ariana Grande kisses friend, shares video
text:
Los Angeles: Singer Ariana Grande "accidentally" shared a video in which she is seen kissing her long time friend Elizabeth Gillies, on social media.


Ariana Grande. Pic/Santa Banta 
In the short video, posted on Instagram, the two friends can been seen puckering up.
  A video posted by Ariana Grande (@arianagrande) onOct 5, 2015 at 10:28pm PDT
"One, two, three," Gillies says before they lean in for a quick kiss, reports mirror.co.uk.
Just as soon as they've smooched, they both pull apart and burst out laughing.
"My favourite video of all time @lizgillz. (p.s. this was totally posted by accident)," Grande wrote next to it.
She also took to Twitter to once again say she did not actually intend to share it with her followers.
"I was editing it in insta to send to her and it posted accidentally but it's great so whatever," Grande wrote.
